---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy - OptyP">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-20 px-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-6">
      At OptyP, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our services.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-6">
      <li>Personal identification information (name, email address, phone number, etc.)</li>
      <li>Profile details provided for resume and LinkedIn optimization</li>
      <li>Usage and analytics data via cookies and similar technologies</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>
      Your information is used solely to provide and improve our services, communicate with you, and comply with legal obligations. We never sell or share your personal data with third parties for marketing without your consent.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">Data Security</h2>
    <p>
      We implement appropriate security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">Your Rights</h2>
    <p>
      You may request access, correction, or deletion of your personal information at any time by contacting us.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      For any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@optyp.com" class="text-primary-600 underline">contact@optyp.com</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
